query:
SELECT 
  ja.id,
  ja.contractorId,
  CONCAT(c.firstName, ' ', c.lastName) as contractorName,
  c.telegramChatId,
  ja.notifiedAt,
  ja.createdAt
FROM jobAssignments ja
LEFT JOIN contractors c ON ja.contractorId = c.id
ORDER BY ja.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10
